reviewText: It does have the Jungle book 1 and 2 as well as Robin hood in Russian. The Jungle book 1 and Robin hood have both the english and Russian version. Whereas the Jungle book 2 only has the russian version. It is a great quality movie, but only works with DVD PAL players. It won't work on my DVD player at home, but it will work on my macbook air and lenovo pc.
